<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A5201001002" page = "2">
<title>
Reverse Shift Prevention Mechanism
</title>
<topic id = "AENAP70A5201001003">
<title>
Construction
</title>
<ptxt>
In the gear shift lever case, the reverse shift limit yoke (2) which turns around reverse shift limit yoke (2) retainer is provided.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
This reverse shift limit yoke (2) restricts the movement of gear shift &#38; select lever (1) to prevent erroneous reverse shifting.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A521054.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "107.472mm" ver = "01" gw = "179" gh = "288"/>
