<topic id = "AENAP70A5201001004">
<title>
Operation
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
If shifting directly from 5th [a] to reverse [b] is attempted, the cubic part of the gear shift &#38; select lever (1) is blocked by the projection of the reverse shift limit yoke (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A520033.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "57.277mm" ver = "02" gw = "224" gh = "146"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
