<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.704in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[c]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
4th
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Then the cubic part of the gear shift &#38; select lever (1) pushes the projection of the reverse shift limit yoke (2). The reverse shift limit yoke (2) rotates and pushes the gear shift &#38; select lever (1) toward the neutral position.
</ptxt>
